snippet.title: Savage: Ultimate Boss Fight PC Gameplay
snippet.description:
DEMO - GTX 1060 6GB | i7-7700 Benchmark * Performance Test 60 FPS 1440p Ultra Graphics | Steam
Game: Savage PC Gameplay
Max FPS: Unlimited
Game on SSD / Streamed with OBS 60FPS
(FPS loss when streaming 4K: 10%~20%)


Savage is a single-player action game that allows players to experience MMORPG-style battles. Many bosses are included this game. Unravel the gimmicks hidden in the attacks, find a strategy, and try to clear the stage.


#Savage #Demo #PC

+ CPU: Intel Core i7 7700 @ 3.60GHz [Undervolted]
+ GPU: NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1060 6GB GDDR5 (PNY) [Overclocked]
+ RAM: 16,0GB (2x8) DDR4 - Dual-Channel @ 2400MHz
+ System: Windows 10
+ Monitor: VG32VQ1B Gamer Asus TUF 31.5', 165 Hz, 2K QHD

+ MSI Afterburner + Rivatuner Statistics Server + CapFrameX + Aida64 FPS Overlay Benchmark
